a continuous ceiling on gross credit to government by the Bank of Ghana (level);   
a floor on the net international reserves of the Bank of Ghana (level);   
a ceiling on wages and salaries;   
a ceiling on the net change in the stock of domestic arrears;   
a ceiling on non-accumulation of new domestic arrears;   
a continuous ceiling on non-accumulation of new external arrears;

a floor on poverty-reducing government expenditures;   
a ceiling on the contracting or guaranteeing of new external concessional debt;   
a ceiling on net domestic assets of Bank of Ghana (level);   
a ceiling on the change in accounts payable of Electricity Company of Ghana (ECG) and Volta River Authority (VRA); and   
a floor on the net after tax profit (excluding government subsidies) of ECG and VRA.
